TITLE: Retrieving Instructions Including Sub-Instructions in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the getAllInstructionsWithSubs helper function to get all instructions including nested sub-instructions from different node types.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/nodes/docs/InstructionNode.md#2025-04-19_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const allInstructionsFromTheRoot = getAllInstructionsWithSubs(rootNode);
const allInstructionsFromThisProgram = getAllInstructionsWithSubs(programNode);
const allInstructionsFromThisInstruction = getAllInstructionsWithSubs(instructionNode);
```

