TITLE: Installing Codama CLI and Initializing Project
DESCRIPTION: Commands to install the Codama package and initialize a new Codama project. This will prompt for the IDL path and script presets.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/cli/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
pnpm install codama
codama init
```

