TITLE: Retrieving All Defined Types Using getAllDefinedTypes Helper in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the getAllDefinedTypes helper function to retrieve all DefinedTypeNodes under a specified node, which can be a RootNode, a ProgramNode, or an array of ProgramNodes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/nodes/docs/ProgramNode.md#2025-04-19_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const allDefinedTypes = getAllDefinedTypes(rootNode);
```

