TITLE: Creating an Instruction for Account Creation in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of creating an instruction that creates a new account, including byte delta information to track account data size changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/nodes/docs/InstructionNode.md#2025-04-19_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
instructionNode({
    name: 'createCounter',
    accounts: [
        instructionAccountNode({ name: 'counter', isWritable: true, isSigner: true }),
        instructionAccountNode({ name: 'authority', isWritable: false, isSigner: false }),
    ],
    byteDeltas: [instructionByteDeltaNode(accountLinkNode('counter'))],
});
```

