TITLE: Updating Accounts in Codama IDL
DESCRIPTION: Updates or deletes AccountNodes based on a configuration object. Supports renaming accounts, renaming fields, adding PDA seeds, and deleting accounts entirely.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/visitors/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
codama.update(
    updateAccountsVisitor({
        vault: {
            // Rename the 'vault' account to 'safe'.
            name: 'safe',
            // Rename the 'owner' field to 'authority'.
            data: { owner: 'authority' },
            // Create a new PDA node and link it to this account.
            seeds: [variablePdaSeedNode('authority', publicKeyTypeNode())],
        },
        counter: {
            // Delete the 'counter' account.
            delete: true,
        },
    }),
);
```

