TITLE: Transforming Defined Types into Accounts in Codama IDL
DESCRIPTION: Transforms DefinedTypeNodes matching specified names into AccountNodes within the same ProgramNode. This visitor allows for conversion of defined types into proper account structures.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/visitors/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
codama.update(transformDefinedTypesIntoAccountsVisitor(['counter', 'escrow']));
```

