TITLE: Creating AccountLinkNode Objects in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of creating AccountLinkNode objects using the helper function. The first example creates a reference to an account in the current program, while the second creates a reference to an account in another program.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/nodes/docs/linkNodes/AccountLinkNode.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const node = accountLinkNode('myAccount');
const nodeFromAnotherProgram = accountLinkNode('myAccount', 'myOtherProgram');
```

