TITLE: Basic Usage of getNodeCodec Function
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the getNodeCodec function to create a codec for a node in a Codama IDL, then using it to encode and decode data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/dynamic-codecs/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
const codec = getNodeCodec([root, program, definedType]);
const bytes = codec.encode(someData);
const decodedData = codec.decode(bytes);
```

