TITLE: Generating Client Code from Codama IDL
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to generate JavaScript and Rust client code from a Codama IDL using renderer visitors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { renderJavaScriptVisitor, renderRustVisitor } from '@codama/renderers';

codama.accept(renderJavaScriptVisitor('clients/js/src/generated', { ... }));
codama.accept(renderRustVisitor('clients/rust/src/generated', { ... }));
```

