TITLE: Writing RenderMap to Filesystem
DESCRIPTION: Example of writing RenderMap content to the filesystem with base directory configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/renderers-core/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const renderMap = new RenderMap()
    .add('programs/token.ts', 'export type TokenProgram = { /* ... */ }')
    .add('accounts/mint.ts', 'export type MintAccount = { /* ... */ }');

renderMap.write('src/generated');
// In this example, files will be written to:
// - src/generated/programs/token.ts
// - src/generated/accounts/mint.ts.
```

