TITLE: PDA Node Example with UTF-8 Constant Seed in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows a practical example of using ConstantPdaSeedNode within a PDA node configuration
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/nodes/docs/pdaSeedNodes/ConstantPdaSeedNode.md#2025-04-19_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
