DESCRIPTION: Example of using the parseInstructionData function to match and deserialize instruction data from a byte array, showing how to access the parsed data and instruction node.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/dynamic-parsers/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_3

