TITLE: Getting All Instruction Arguments with Helper Function in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the getAllInstructionArguments helper function to retrieve all arguments of an instruction including extra arguments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/nodes/docs/InstructionNode.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

