TITLE: Running Codama Scripts with CLI
DESCRIPTION: Examples of using the 'codama run' command to execute Codama scripts. Shows options for running specific scripts or all scripts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/codama-idl/codama/blob/main/packages/cli/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
codama run         # Only runs your before visitors.
codama run js rust # Runs your before visitors followed by the `js` and `rust` scripts.
codama run --all   # Runs your before visitors followed by all your scripts.
```

