TITLE: Defining a Character Histogram MapTypeNode in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a MapTypeNode for a character histogram, using single UTF-8 characters as keys, 16-bit unsigned integers as values, and a u8 prefixed count for the map length.
