TITLE: Recording Linkables on First Visit in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: The recordLinkablesOnFirstVisitVisitor function combines interceptFirstVisitVisitor and getRecordLinkablesVisitor to record all linkable nodes before the first visit of any node in the AST.
